dip.gui.swing

Class AssocJComboBox.AssociatedObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • dip.gui.swing.AssocJComboBox.AssociatedObj
  • Enclosing class:
    AssocJComboBox

    public static class AssocJComboBox.AssociatedObj
extends java.lang.Object
    Associates a given Value with a given String. This is essentially a name-value pair, and is useful for localizing internal program constants (Strings, Enums, ints, etc.) to a value suitable for UI display.

    The Value object needs to have a constant toString() representation for persitence to work properly.

    Note: this class has a natural ordering that is inconsistent with equals
